      "translated_from": "ruRU",
      "translation_date": "2026-04-23T12:26:49.7283152Z",
      "original_text": "\"И как же мне подготовиться?\"",
      "traits": [
        {
          "trait": "Translated",
          "trait_date": "2026-04-17T13:07:44.1162733Z",
          "locale_text": "\"And how do you suggest I prepare myself?\""
        },
        {
          "trait": "Edited",
          "trait_date": "2026-04-23T12:26:49.7283160Z",
          "locale_text": "\"And how do you suggest I prepare myself?\""
        },
        {
          "trait": "AD_tr_ed",
          "trait_date": "2025-11-11T07:48:31.1031211Z",
          "locale_text": "\"I'm not here for that. I care not for your ancient oaths.\""
        },
        {
          "trait": "TK_tr",
          "trait_date": "2026-04-17T13:07:44.1162752Z",
          "locale_text": "\"And how do you suggest I prepare myself?\""
