          "locale_text": "\"And how do you suggest I prepare myself?\""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "locale": "jaJP",
      "text": "「そのために来たのではない。そなたの古き忠誓など意に介さぬ」",
      "modification_date": "2025-11-12T12:36:13.1666473Z",
      "translated_from": "enGB",
      "translation_date": "2025-11-11T09:57:03.0988414Z",
      "original_text": "\"I'm not here for that. I care not for your ancient oaths.\"",
      "traits": [
        {
          "trait": "Translated",
          "trait_date": "2025-11-11T09:57:03.0988421Z",
          "locale_text": "「そのために来たのではない。そなたの古き忠誓など意に介さぬ。」"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "locale": "frFR",
      "text": "« Et comment suggérez-vous que je m'y prépare ? »",
      "modification_date": "2026-05-06T08:02:26.7317012Z",
      "translated_from": "enGB",
      "translation_date": "2026-05-06T08:02:26.7317013Z",
      "original_text": "\"And how do you suggest I prepare myself?\"",
      "traits": [
        {
          "trait": "Translated",
          "trait_date": "2026-05-06T08:02:26.7317021Z",
          "locale_text": "« Et comment suggérez-vous que je m'y prépare ? »"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "locale": "trTR",
      "text": "\"Nasıl hazırlanmamı önerirsin?\"",
      "modification_date": "2026-05-06T08:04:42.4275198Z",
      "translated_from": "enGB",
      "translation_date": "2026-05-06T08:04:42.4275199Z",
      "original_text": "\"And how do you suggest I prepare myself?\"",
      "traits": [
        {
          "trait": "Translated",
          "trait_date": "2026-05-06T08:04:42.4275204Z",
          "locale_text": "\"Nasıl hazırlanmamı önerirsin?\""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "locale": "deDE",
      "text": "\"Und wie soll ich mich Eurer Meinung nach vorbereiten?\"",
